OL,4,Capproach to racist and sectarian
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FStormont's leaders called for a zero-
OL,8,Ftolerance approach to racist and
OL,9,Fsectarian attacks as they voiced
OL,10,Fsupport for tougher prison sentences
OL,11,Ffor perpetrators.
OL,13,FThose guilty of violence against women
OL,14,Fand girls should also spend longer in
OL,15,Fjail, First Minister Michelle O'Neill
OL,16,Fand deputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,17,FPengelly said.
