OL,4,Capproach to racist and sectarian
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FThey made the comments after all
OL,8,Fministers in Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Fdevolved powersharing agreed a joint
OL,10,Fstatement condemning recent sectarian
OL,11,Fand racist attacks.
OL,13,FThe statement branded the acts of
OL,14,Fintimidation as "abhorrent" and
OL,15,Fexpressed solidarity with victims and
OL,16,Ftheir families. It stressed the need
OL,17,Ffor a "zero tolerance approach" and
OL,18,Fcalled for calm across all communities.
OL,20,F"All acts of intimidation must stop
OL,21,Fimmediately," it said.
