OL,7,FPolice figures show that racist hate
OL,8,Fcrimes in Northern Ireland have
OL,9,Freached record levels, with 2,049 race
OL,10,Fincidents and 1,329 race crimes in the
OL,11,F12 months from July 1 last year to
OL,12,FJune 30 this year.
OL,14,FThose annual figures are the highest
OL,15,Fsince such data began to be collated
OL,16,Fand reported by the PSNI in 2004/05.
OL,18,FRates spiked significantly in 2024/25,
OL,19,Fwith 646 more race incidents and 434
OL,20,Fmore race crimes recorded compared
OL,21,Fwith the previous 12 months.
