OL,7,FWhile Belfast has seen the most
OL,8,Fattacks, the Co Antrim town of
OL,9,FBallymena has also witnessed a surge
OL,10,Fin race-related violence, included a
OL,11,Fspate of anti-immigration rioting in
OL,12,FJune.
OL,14,FA number of cars belonging to members
OL,15,Fof Ballymena's Filipino community were
OL,16,Fset on fire and destroyed in the
OL,17,Flatest attack on Sunday while recent
OL,18,Fweeks have also brought reports of
OL,19,Fvigilant gangs confronting people from
OL,20,Fethnic minority communities in parts
OL,21,Fof Belfast.
