OL,7,FThe first meeting of the Executive
OL,8,Fsince recess also came after a summer
OL,9,Fthat has seen several females lose
OL,10,Ftheir lives in violent circumstances
OL,11,Fin Northern Ireland. Incidents
OL,12,Fincluded the murder of a mother and
OL,13,Fher two children in their Co Fermanagh
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FVanessa Whyte, 45, and her children
OL,17,FJames Rutledge, 14, and Sara Rutledge,
OL,18,F13, died in a shooting at their house
OL,19,Fin Maguiresbridge in July.
