OL,7,FAgricultural contractor Ian Rutledge,
OL,8,F43, who also died in the incident, is
OL,9,Funderstood to be the only suspect in
OL,10,Fthe shooting of his family.
OL,12,FThe recent racist and sectarian
OL,13,Fattacks and the challenge of tackling
OL,14,Fviolence against women and girls were
OL,15,Fall discussed during Thursday's
OL,16,FExecutive meeting at Stormont Castle
OL,17,Fin Belfast.
