OL,7,FOn the racist and sectarian
OL,8,Fintimidation, Ms O'Neill said
OL,9,Fafterwards that "political leadership"
OL,10,Fwas needed.
OL,12,F"Political leadership is required to
OL,13,Fsend out that message that we will not
OL,14,Faccept this behaviour, and it does not
OL,15,Freflect the vast majority of society,"
OL,16,Fshe said.
