OL,7,F"In my opinion, there's a small
OL,8,Fminority of people who are causing
OL,9,Fhavoc, and it needs to be dealt with
OL,10,Fat a criminal level in terms of
OL,11,Fpolicing response, but also then
OL,12,Fjudiciary and everything else.
OL,14,F"So we need to throw everything that
OL,15,Fwe have to ensure we create a society
OL,16,Fthat's inclusive and welcoming."
