OL,7,FThe Sinn Fein vice president added:
OL,8,F"This is our first Executive meeting
OL,9,Fsince the recess. So it was important
OL,10,Fthat we collectively and all parties
OL,11,Fin the Executive send this united
OL,12,Ffront message today that we stand
OL,13,Funequivocally together in saying no to
OL,14,Fracism and no to sectarianism. I think
OL,15,Fthat's a crucial message that we
OL,16,Fcollectively want to deliver today."
OL,18,FDUP deputy First Minister Ms Little-
OL,19,FPengelly said the intimidation and
OL,20,Fviolence was "totally unacceptable".
