OL,7,F"Any threat or any intimidation of any
OL,8,Fperson in Northern Ireland is
OL,9,Fabsolutely wrong, no matter what that
OL,10,Fis motivated by," she said.
OL,12,F"By issuing an Executive statement
OL,13,Ftoday, we are demonstrating our
OL,14,Fdetermination to work together to
OL,15,Fensure that people can be safe."
OL,17,FMs Little-Pengelly said the racist
OL,18,Fattacks were not just an issue for
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland and were also
OL,20,F"playing out on the streets" across
OL,21,Fthe UK, Ireland "and beyond".
