OL,7,F"The issue of immigration is not going
OL,8,Fto go away. I believe that this will
OL,9,Fcontinue to be a key issue of
OL,10,Fdiscussion," she added.
OL,12,FThe deputy First Minister said many
OL,13,Fpeople have "genuine concerns" and are
OL,14,F"frustrated" with "irregular
OL,15,Fmigration", but added: "I think it's
OL,16,Fincredibly important that the Northern
OL,17,FIreland Executives makes clear that a
OL,18,Fdiscussion or a debate about
OL,19,Fimmigration is entirely separate from
OL,20,Fany threat or intimidation which is
OL,21,Fcompletely wrong and never justified."
